export function getTableWithName(name) {
  console.log("GetTableWithName: ", name);
  for (let i = 0; i < tables.length; i += 1) {
    const table = tables[i];
    if (table.name === name) {
      console.log("Found table: ", table);
      return table;
    }
  }
  console.error("Table not found: ", name);
  return null;
}
